        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n\\)</span> est divisible\npar <span class=\"math inline\">\\((X-1)(X-2)\\)</span> et que le quotient\nest <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Q_2-Q_1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
